  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Category: General </p><p>Prerequisite: Proficiency with Medium Armor, Level 4+ </p><p>You have trained to master the use of heavy armor, gaining the following benefits: </p><p>• You gain proficiency with heavy armor.</p><p> If you are already proficient with heavy armor, instead increase your Strength or Constitution score by 1, to a maximum of 20.</p><p>• Select 4 Damage types from the following list; Earth, Wind, Fire, Cold, Lightning, Force, Acid, Poison, Necrotic.</p><p> Heavy armor you wear applies its Reinforced value vs the chosen damage types.</p><p></p>",
